Package io.github.yvasyliev.telegramforwarderbot.service.command

Interface MessageCommand

All Known Implementing Classes:
HelpMessageCommand, StopCommand
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface MessageCommand
Functional interface for executing commands based on Telegram messages. Implementations should define how to handle a given message.
